              <p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">案例一：14海宁债发行人转股意愿弱，债券持有</strong></p>
            </section>
            <section style="border-top-width: 2px; border-top-style: dotted; width: 100%; border-top-color: rgb(163, 116, 54); box-sizing: border-box;"></section>
